Continental to Invest in Emerging Markets Tire Business, HB Says

-- B y   A l l i s o n   C o n n o l l y
-- 
2011-05-12T19:19:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-12/continental-to-invest-in-emerging-markets-tire-business-hb-says.html
     May 12 (Bloomberg) -- Continental AG (CON)  plans to invest more
than 1 billion euros in the tire business in the coming years,
particularly in emerging markets, Handelsblatt said in a preview
of a story to be published tomorrow, citing comments from board
member Nikolai Setzer.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Allison Connolly in  Frankfurt  at 
 aconnolly4@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at   pserafino@bloomberg.net . 